data.description: Great house in prime location in Cherry Creek schools. Space galore with 4 bedrooms upstairs, one bedroom on main level (or could be used as a study) and one bedroom in the basement, with an additional study or work room. Kitchen has been tastefully remodeled with high end appliances. Counter seating and table seating in the kitchen area. Master bath has been remodeled with inviting oversize shower. Furnace was replaced in 2021. New plantation shutters with dual openings in the front. Enjoy entertaining in the gorgeous backyard on the large trex deck under the trees. Back yard is almost maintenance free with turf yard. The oversized 3 car garage is almost 1000 square feet- room for all your necessities. 75 gallon water heater so you can use all 4 showers simultaneously! Access to Centennial's Ting super fast fiber optic internet service. Community pool. Huge opportunity to get into this neighborhood at a lower price-point. The basement does need some work. Get with your favorite realtor to see this home.
